^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Let's talk about the auction. Some people do like to open light in third seat, so, if you play that way, Nada can bid 1C. She has a good suit and doesn't mind it being led. So, she has a reason to open 1C. I personally like to use rule of 20 for all 4 seats. That way, even in 3rd seat, I have some idea of the values partner has, and will not be afraid to bid thin games. Therefore, my style is rule of 20 in all 4 seats, but there are arguments to be made for opening light in third seat.|
