NT||cp|8|AT|
^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Now, as to the play. Nada had the right idea about not drawing trumps too early, but she can make a trick or 2 more. Instead of even starting with clubs, she should keep control of all suits and just start with hearts right away. She ends up losing 2 hearts, 1 spade, and 1 diamond for sure. Once you knock out the hearts, you can draw trumps. You might lose another spade, on a heart ruff, but you will always make at least 2 and 3 much of the time.|
